          "value": "<p>When a polong damages a living creature with its spectral hand Strike, the target must succeed a @Check[type:fortitude|dc:30] save or become @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Drained]{Drained 1} and take [[/r {1d8}[persistent,bleed]]]{1d8} @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Persistent Damage]{Persistent bleed Damage}. Further damage increases the drained condition value by 1 and the persistent bleed damage by 1d8 to a maximum value of drained 4 and [[/r {4d8}[persistent,bleed]]]{4d8} @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Persistent Damage]{Persistent bleed Damage}.</p>"
